OL,7,FA killer who inflicted more than 100
OL,8,Finjuries including fractures and
OL,9,Fcigarette burns on his partner had
OL,10,Fjust got out of prison for assaulting
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FStephen Todd left "tiny" Melissa
OL,14,FEastick, who was frail and vulnerable,
OL,15,Fwith around 123 bruises, cuts,
OL,16,Ffractures and cigarette burns, which
OL,17,Fwere caused during repeated assaults
OL,18,Fat his home.
