OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court heard 36-year-
OL,8,Fold Melissa had also suffered a brain
OL,9,Finjury which would have left her
OL,10,Funconscious for "some days" before her
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FTodd, 41, denied murder and was being
OL,14,Ftried by a jury at Newcastle Crown
OL,15,FCourt.
OL,17,FHowever, on the second day of the
OL,18,Ftrial on Wednesday (23 October),
OL,19,Fbefore the case got underway, Todd
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to the charge. He will
OL,21,Fbe sentenced at a later date.
