OL,7,FAfter Todd's courtroom confession,
OL,8,Fprosecutor Peter Glenser KC told the
OL,9,Fcourt: "He had just been released from
OL,10,Fprison in relation to an assault on
OL,11,Fher, weeks before."
OL,13,FMr Glenser said Melissa was a frail
OL,14,Fand vulnerable woman and added: "She
OL,15,Fwas tiny".
OL,17,FHe told the court Melissa had been
OL,18,Fbeaten with enough force to fracture
OL,19,Fbones on three occasions over several
OL,20,Fdays before she was eventually killed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/16
