OL,7,FThe court heard Todd had called 999 at
OL,8,Fjust after 7am on 17 October last year
OL,9,Fand reported he was unable to wake
OL,10,FMelissa, who did not appear to be
OL,11,Fbreathing.
OL,13,FThe emergency call handler advised
OL,14,FTodd to get Melissa onto the floor and
OL,15,Fgave him instructions on how to carry
OL,16,Fout CPR, which he did.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/16
