OL,7,FWhen paramedics arrived at his then
OL,8,Fhome at Stockton Terrace, Sunderland,
OL,9,FTodd led them to a dark living room
OL,10,Fand claimed: "She was alright
OL,11,Fyesterday."
OL,13,FBut Mr Glenser said: "The Crown, the
OL,14,Fprosecution, say that, like a great
OL,15,Fdeal of what he was to say over the
OL,16,Fdays that followed, was a lie.
OL,18,F"There was no way that Melissa Eastick
OL,19,Fwas 'alright yesterday', the day
OL,20,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/16
