OL,7,F"It very quickly became apparent that
OL,8,Fthere was very extensive bruising and
OL,9,Fswelling to her body and face and that
OL,10,Fshe was very cold to the touch.
OL,12,F"When they examined her it was obvious
OL,13,Fshe was dead and her life was formally
OL,14,Fpronounced extinct at 7.14am.
OL,16,F"It appears that her death was neither
OL,17,Fquick nor easy. She had sustained more
OL,18,Fthan 100 injuries, probably nearer 123
OL,19,Fin the time leading up to her death.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/16
