OL,7,F"When she died she was 36 years old.
OL,8,FShe was a frail and vulnerable
OL,9,Findividual."
OL,11,FThe court heard Melissa was in Todd's
OL,12,Fcompany on 2 October and they were
OL,13,Fcaught on CCTV together in Asda, where
OL,14,Fthey bought food before they returned
OL,15,Fto his two-bedroom flat.
OL,17,FMr Glenser told jurors: "There are no
OL,18,Frecorded sightings of Melissa Eastick
OL,19,Falive after this date, either in
OL,20,Fperson or on CCTV."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/16
