OL,7,FJurors heard Melissa received a sales
OL,8,Fcall on her mobile from Vodaphone on
OL,9,FOctober 6, which was recorded by the
OL,10,Fcompany and showed that she did have a
OL,11,Fconversation with the employee.
OL,13,FMr Glenser said that call was the
OL,14,F"last proof of life for Melissa
OL,15,FEastick".
