OL,7,FThe court heard when the emergency
OL,8,Fservices arrived at the flat on the
OL,9,F17th, Melissa had facial bruising,
OL,10,Ffractured ribs, vertebrae, nose and
OL,11,Fjaw, cigarette burns to her torso and
OL,12,Fhad a brain injury which would have
OL,13,Frendered her unconscious for some days
OL,14,Fbefore her death.
OL,16,FMr Glenser said some of the injuries
OL,17,Fwould have been inflicted between four
OL,18,Fand seven days before her death
OL,19,Fwhereas others were about 72 hours
OL,20,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/16
