OL,7,FThe court heard Todd and Melissa had
OL,8,Fbeen partners "on and off" since
OL,9,Faround 2018 and both had struggles
OL,10,Fwith alcohol.
OL,12,FMr Glenser said their relationship had
OL,13,Fbeen "turbulent to say the least" and
OL,14,FMelissa had spent time living in a
OL,15,Fhomeless shelter but it appeared she
OL,16,Fwas staying with Todd from around last
OL,17,FAugust.
OL,19,FTodd, 41, of Buttermere Street,
OL,20,FSunderland, will be sentenced in
OL,21,Faround two weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/16
