OL,7,FHe told police Melissa had arrived at
OL,8,Fhis home a few days before her death
OL,9,Fand was already "black and blue" but
OL,10,Fhad denied responsibility for any of
OL,11,Fher injuries.
OL,13,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,14,FChief Inspector Louise Jenkins, of
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police, said: "First and
OL,16,Fforemost, I would like to extend my
OL,17,Fdeepest sympathies to Melissa's family
OL,18,Fand loved ones ` and we will continue
OL,19,Fto offer them any support they need.
