OL,7,F"This is a truly horrific case where a
OL,8,Fyoung woman has sadly lost her life at
OL,9,Fthe hands of her partner.
OL,11,F"Todd initially denied any involvement
OL,12,Fin Melissa's death ` despite her
OL,13,Fsustaining more than 100 injuries.
OL,15,F"He has shown no remorse throughout
OL,16,Fthe investigation.
