OL,7,F"However, thanks to the weight of
OL,8,Fevidence against him, Todd has finally
OL,9,Fadmitted his guilt and Melissa's loved
OL,10,Fones can now attempt to navigate life
OL,11,Fwithout her."
OL,13,FDet Chief Insp Jenkins added: "I'd
OL,14,Flike to thank all the officers and
OL,15,Fstaff, and criminal justice partners
OL,16,Fwho helped with this complex
OL,17,Finvestigation and have ultimately
OL,18,Fhelped us secure justice for Melissa.
